answers.answer: Oh Yes I have had anxiety since the beginning for so many reasons. Now I worry about labor and delivery... I think since I've been through it once already I know what to expect and it terrifies me. But at the same time I'm ready to get it over with.
I keep thinking iv been blessed with an amazong child will I be blessed again. Not a good feeling. X
With my 6 yr old son I had a C-section so with my little one now I'm having a VBAC... So I'm nervous as heck lol.

I'm nervous as well. This is my third. I keep asking myself if I'm crazy to be doing this all over again, natural birth the first two and plan on it again this time. With my second I went into labor at 39 weeks. So I'm wondering if I will have this one early or not. Getting more nervous each day but excited for it to be over with.

It looks like there is a few of us feeling  the  same  way  i though  i was thinking  too much. I get anxiety  nervous.  Had my daughther  15 years  ago. I had preeclampsia  was induced at 37 weeks. No pain medication.  It was allot of hours  with  her one thing  right  after another.  Now 35 weeks and hoping  this  one  will be  better

question: As the day comes closer I start thinking of everything that can go wrong and worrying constantly. With my daughter I was not scared at all so this is new to me.
title: Any other second time moms having anxiety?
